LABEL: 0x3b44
JPN: 「本番で歓声を受けながら泳ぐと、決まってフォームがバラバラになって……もう、ダメだった」
ENG: "But when it came time for the real deal, when I heard all those cheers around me, my form fell apart. I just couldn't do it anymore."

LABEL: 0x3bb6
JPN: 「最初は、皆が応援してくれた」
ENG: "Everyone supported me, at first."

LABEL: 0x3bee
ENG: "They waited for me."

LABEL: 0x3c18
JPN: 「でも、事態は悪くなる一方だった」
ENG: "But it just kept getting worse and worse."

LABEL: 0x3c54
JPN: 「だんだん、皆、どう俺に接したらいいか……分からなくなっていったんだと思う」
ENG: "And eventually, nobody knew how they were supposed to face me anymore."

LABEL: 0x3cba
ENG: "I didn't even know how to face myself."

LABEL: 0x3ce2
ENG: "Everything was so stifling."

LABEL: 0x3d14
ENG: "I felt like I was going to suffocate."

LABEL: 0x3d42
ENG: "And so..."

LABEL: 0x3d6c
ENG: "I quit the club."

LABEL: 0x3d98
JPN: 「それからはろくでもない毎日だった」
ENG: "I wasted day after day on the most pointless crap."

LABEL: 0x3e78
JPN: 家では、学校に真面目に通っているふりをして。
ENG: At home, I'd act like I was still going to school.

LABEL: 0x3eb4
JPN: クラブを続けているふりをして。
ENG: Like I was still participating in the club.

LABEL: 0x3ee2
JPN: 嘘を吐くことに慣れていく。
ENG: I got used to spitting out those same old lies.

LABEL: 0x3f0c
ENG: My father was strict.

LABEL: 0x3f28
ENG: My mother believed in me.

LABEL: 0x3f4a
JPN: スポーツマンで、素直な息子。
ENG: To them, I was their honest, sports-loving son.

LABEL: 0x3f76
JPN: 実際は学校に行くふりをして、町に出て……
ENG: But in reality I'd just pretend to go to school, then wander into town instead.

LABEL: 0x3fae
ENG: I'd roam the streets.

LABEL: 0x3fcc
JPN: 同じようにぶらぶらしている連中とつるむようになって。
ENG: I'd hang out with all the other truants.

LABEL: 0x4010
JPN: そのうちばれると思っていたけど、１年間もそんな状態が続いた。
ENG: I figured I'd get caught before too long, but a whole year passed, and nothing changed.

LABEL: 0x40d8
ENG: One day.

LABEL: 0x40f0
ENG: "So this is where you've been."

LABEL: 0x4116
ENG: "They're really throwing down over there."

LABEL: 0x4144
ENG: "Come back us up."

LABEL: 0x416a
JPN: 何が待っているのかは何となく分かっていた。
ENG: I pretty much knew what was waiting for me.

LABEL: 0x41a4
JPN: 行ってはいけないと、誰かが言ったような気がした。
ENG: I thought I heard someone shouting at me, telling me to stop.

LABEL: 0x41e4
ENG: "Hey, what do you punks think you're doing!?"

LABEL: 0x4216
ENG: The police came running.

LABEL: 0x4238
ENG: "Let's get outta here!"

LABEL: 0x427c
ENG: "Takahara!!"

LABEL: 0x429e
JPN: 俺はそこにとどまり続けた。
ENG: I just stood there. I didn't move an inch.

LABEL: 0x42c8
JPN: もう、逃げるのはごめんだった。
ENG: I was sick of running away.

LABEL: 0x42f6
JPN: いっそ全部ぶっ壊れてしまえ――
ENG: I thought I should just bring it all down.

LABEL: 0x4324
ENG: I'd tear it down from the ground up.

LABEL: 0x4348
ENG: It felt great. Refreshing.

LABEL: 0x436c
JPN: これでとにかく、この袋小路みたいな状況をぶっ壊せる。
ENG: No matter what happened, I thought I'd at least break my way out of the rut I was stuck in.

LABEL: 0x43b0
ENG: I was sure of it.

LABEL: 0x4412
ENG: "I was suspended."

LABEL: 0x443a
JPN: 「もちろん、家族の知るところになった」
ENG: "Couldn't keep that one from my parents, of course."

LABEL: 0x447a
JPN: 「俺はどこかで、うすうす両親はいろんなことに気づいているんじゃないかって思ってた」
ENG: "I sort of figured they already had a vague idea what I'd been up to lately."

LABEL: 0x44e6
ENG: "I mean, they are my parents."

LABEL: 0x4512
ENG: "But turns out I was wrong."

LABEL: 0x4546
ENG: "It caught them completely off guard."

LABEL: 0x457c
JPN: 「俺が想像したよりもずっとショックが大きかったらしい」
ENG: "They took it worse than I'd ever imagined."

LABEL: 0x45cc
JPN: 「父親が母親を、母親が父親を責め合って」
ENG: "My dad blamed my mom, and my mom blamed my dad."

LABEL: 0x460e
ENG: "Our family fell apart."

LABEL: 0x4644
JPN: 「その中心にいて、俺は何もできなかった」
ENG: "It was all my fault, and I couldn't do a damn thing."

LABEL: 0x4686
ENG: "I just drifted through it all in a daze."

LABEL: 0x46be
JPN: 「学校は夏休みに入り、俺は家にこもっていた」
ENG: "And before I knew it, summer vacation arrived. I just holed myself up at home."

LABEL: 0x4704
JPN: 「ある日……二階の部屋から降りていくと、リビングで父親が１人で新聞を読んでいた」
ENG: "One day... I wandered downstairs and ran into my dad. He was sitting in the living room, reading a newspaper."

LABEL: 0x476e
JPN: 「俺は冷蔵庫に置いてある朝食を取り出そうとした」
ENG: "I went to grab my breakfast from the fridge."

LABEL: 0x47b8
JPN: 「そしたら親父が新聞を置いて、こっちを見た」
ENG: "Then my dad put down his newspaper and looked at me."

LABEL: 0x47fe
ENG: "And... he said this."

LABEL: 0x489a
ENG: 'You know this is all your fault, don't you?'

LABEL: 0x48ce
JPN: チームが敗退したのも。
ENG: My swim team losing...

LABEL: 0x48f4
JPN: 学校にいられなくなったのも。
ENG: Losing my will to go to school...

LABEL: 0x4920
ENG: People getting hurt...

LABEL: 0x4942
JPN: 家族がばらばらになったのも。
ENG: My family falling apart...

LABEL: 0x496e
ENG: All of that was my fault?

LABEL: 0x498e
JPN: きっと、その通りなんだろう。
ENG: I knew he was probably right.

LABEL: 0x49ba
JPN: その通りすぎて、直視できなくて。
ENG: I knew it so well, I couldn't look him in the eye.

LABEL: 0x49ea
JPN: その有様から目を逸らして、俺は逃げてきた。
ENG: So I blinded myself to the truth and ran.

LABEL: 0x4a24
JPN: いくらその通りだからって、正論だからって、受け止められるほど強くはないから。
ENG: No matter how much I knew he was right, no matter what arguments he subjected me to, I wasn't strong enough to accept it.

LABEL: 0x4aa6
JPN: 「とにかく、あそこから離れたかった」
ENG: "I just wanted to get away from there, whatever it took."

LABEL: 0x4ae4
JPN: 「離れてどうにかなるわけじゃないって分かっていても」
ENG: "I knew that getting away wouldn't fix anything, but I still wanted to."

LABEL: 0x4b32
JPN: 「だから鏡子さんからの手紙につられて、こんなところまで来た」
ENG: "So I got lured in by Kyouko-san's letter, and came all the way out here."

LABEL: 0x4b88
JPN: 「そしたら思いがけず楽しくて」
ENG: "And somehow, being here was just so much fun..."

LABEL: 0x4bc0
ENG: "...I couldn't bring myself to go home."

LABEL: 0x4c0e
ENG: "But I'll go back."

LABEL: 0x4c36
ENG: "When tomorrow's festival's over, and everyone's safe."

LABEL: 0x4c6a
ENG: "I'll go home."

LABEL: 0x4c90
JPN: 「やり残したことがたくさんある」
ENG: "There's tons of stuff I still have to do."

LABEL: 0x4cca
JPN: 「逃げてきたことがたくさんあるんだ」
ENG: "There are still so many things I ran away from."

LABEL: 0x4d08
ENG: "Don't you have anything like that, Shiroha?"

LABEL: 0x4d3e
ENG: "Something you still have to do on this island?"

LABEL: 0x4d76
ENG: "Something you want to do, starting now?"

LABEL: 0x4da8
JPN: 「自分１人ならいなくなってもいいなんて言うなよ」
ENG: "And don't give me any of that 'I don't mind if I die' talk."

LABEL: 0x4df2
ENG: "At the very least, for me..."

LABEL: 0x4e1e
JPN: 「しろはが、この島にいて救われた」
ENG: "...You were my saving grace on this island."

LABEL: 0x4e5a
ENG: "I'm glad you were here."

LABEL: 0x4ec4
ENG: "Hairi..."

LABEL: 0x4eec
JPN: 「この前、それを言いたかった」
ENG: "That's what I wanted to say last time."

LABEL: 0x4f24
ENG: "When I said I had a lot to thank you for."

LABEL: 0x4f52
ENG: "Your cooking was delicious."

LABEL: 0x4f80
JPN: 「誰かのために作ってあげろよ」
ENG: "So go whip something up for someone!"

LABEL: 0x4fb8
JPN: 「そのたびに誰かが笑顔になるぞ」
ENG: "That's all it'll take to put a smile on their face."

LABEL: 0x4ff2
ENG: "They'll be overjoyed, I promise."

LABEL: 0x5022
ENG: "Just like I was..."

LABEL: 0x504e
JPN: 「そんな未来がなくなるなんて、もったいないだろ」
ENG: "Letting a future like that slip away would be a waste, wouldn't it?"

LABEL: 0x50ca
ENG: "So go back. Go home."

LABEL: 0x50fa
ENG: "Everyone's waiting for you."

LABEL: 0x512e
ENG: "...So go home."

LABEL: 0x51bc
ENG: "Are you crying?"

LABEL: 0x51e6
ENG: "...No way."

LABEL: 0x5254
ENG: "Sorry."

LABEL: 0x5278
ENG: "For what?"

LABEL: 0x52ac
ENG: "I don't know, but..."

LABEL: 0x52d8
ENG: "Sorry."

LABEL: 0x531e
ENG: "Let's get going."

LABEL: 0x535a
ENG: "Wait!"

LABEL: 0x53ae
ENG: "It'll happen any minute now."

LABEL: 0x53ea
ENG: "I want you to see it, too."

LABEL: 0x5416
ENG: "*Stare*..."

LABEL: 0x544c
ENG: "Not me!"

LABEL: 0x5476
ENG: "Then, what?"

LABEL: 0x54aa
ENG: "Look around me."

LABEL: 0x54d2
ENG: "Around you?"

LABEL: 0x5512
ENG: What? It's just a beach, what's she...

LABEL: 0x559c
ENG: Huh?

LABEL: 0x5664
ENG: "Are those...?"

LABEL: 0x56bc
ENG: "Fireflies."

LABEL: 0x56dc
ENG: "Seriously?"

LABEL: 0x56fe
JPN: 「蛍って、山にいるものじゃないのか」
ENG: "Aren't those supposed to live in the mountains?"

LABEL: 0x573c
ENG: "Sea-fireflies."

LABEL: 0x5764
JPN: どこかで、聞いたことがある。
ENG: I felt like I'd heard that name somewhere before.

LABEL: 0x5790
ENG: The fireflies of the sea...

LABEL: 0x57b0
ENG: "It's like the beach is glowing."

LABEL: 0x5806
ENG: "Yeah."

LABEL: 0x5862
ENG: "This place..."

LABEL: 0x58b0
JPN: 「昔おとーさんに教えてもらった」
ENG: "My father showed it to me, a long time ago."

LABEL: 0x58ea
ENG: "It's a bit of a secret."

LABEL: 0x5912
JPN: 「ずっと、光らなくなってたの」
ENG: "It didn't light up for a really long time."

LABEL: 0x594a
JPN: 「けど、今年の夏……また光ったの」
ENG: "But, this summer... It started glowing again."

LABEL: 0x5986
ENG: "For the first time in ten years."

LABEL: 0x59b0
ENG: "Ten years!?"

LABEL: 0x59d8
ENG: "I've got some pretty crazy luck then, huh?"

LABEL: 0x5a10
ENG: "...Yeah."

LABEL: 0x5a7e
ENG: "Um, you see..."

LABEL: 0x5aa2
JPN: 「昔、未来に行きたいって思ってたことがある」
ENG: "A long time ago, I wanted to go to the future."

LABEL: 0x5ae8
ENG: "To the future? Why?"

LABEL: 0x5b16
ENG: "Probably because I was sick of waiting."

LABEL: 0x5b4c
JPN: 「いくら待ってもダメだから」
ENG: "No matter how long I waited, it never worked out."

LABEL: 0x5b82
JPN: 「時間を早送りして、会いに行きたいって思った」
ENG: "I wanted to fast-forward through time, so I could finally see them again."

LABEL: 0x5c12
ENG: "Maybe..."

LABEL: 0x5c3c
JPN: 「未来に行きたいって思ってたから、未来が見えるようになったのかな」
ENG: "I ended up seeing the future because of how badly I wanted to go there."

LABEL: 0x5cba
ENG: "Do you still want to go?"

LABEL: 0x5d0c
ENG: "Nope."

LABEL: 0x5d30
JPN: 「いつまで待ったらいいか分からないし」
ENG: "I don't know how long I'd have to wait, anyway."

LABEL: 0x5d70
ENG: "So I'm done with that."

LABEL: 0x5d9e
JPN: 「なにも見えなくてもいいのに」
ENG: "I'd rather not see anything at all."

LABEL: 0x5dfe
JPN: 「いつか一緒に、いろんなところに行こう」
ENG: "Let's go explore all over the place together, someday."

LABEL: 0x5e66
ENG: "Hairi..."

LABEL: 0x5e8e
ENG: "Like where?"

LABEL: 0x5eb4
ENG: "Huh?"

LABEL: 0x5ed6
ENG: "Where's 'all over the place'?"

LABEL: 0x5f2a
JPN: 「なんとなく言ってみただけで……具体的には……」
ENG: "It sorta just came to me in the moment. I don't really have, like, a specific plan..."

LABEL: 0x5f9a
JPN: 「いろんなところって言われても……返事しかねる」
ENG: "I can't give you a reply if 'all over the place' is the best you can do."

LABEL: 0x5fe4
JPN: 「そこはなんとなく返事しておけばいいじゃないか」
ENG: "You could at least give me a vague reply, right?"

LABEL: 0x6054
ENG: "I can't be vague about something like this!"

LABEL: 0x6088
JPN: 「変なところに連れて行かれたら嫌だ」
ENG: "What if you took me somewhere weird? That would be terrible."

LABEL: 0x60c6
JPN: 「連れていくかっ。人をなんだと思ってる」
ENG: "Of course I wouldn't do that! What kind of person do you think I am?"

LABEL: 0x6108
ENG: "A weird one."

LABEL: 0x612c
ENG: "Oh, come on!"

LABEL: 0x6200
ENG: "Let's go home."

LABEL: 0x6224
ENG: "Yeah."

LABEL: 0x62ec
ENG: "I'm... sorry..."

LABEL: 0x636c
ENG: "Welcome back."

LABEL: 0x6390
ENG: "Welcome back."

LABEL: 0x63b2
ENG: "Welcome back."

LABEL: 0x63d6
ENG: "Welcome back."

LABEL: 0x64d2
ENG: "I'm back!"
